snippet.title: Boom Boom Rocket Rave New World Endurance Hard
snippet.description: Just thought I'd post a run I did on BBR today, just wanted to see how well I did after not playing this game for about a year. Not too shabby it turns out. This score also topped the highest score this week at the posting time of this video although 278th isn't that bad. Lost my nerve a few times which resulted in a few misses but I don't consider myself MLG!!11!! at this game so I won't get big headed about it. Anyway, enjoy.
